nullum crimen, nulla poena sine praevia.data-term: nullum crimen, nulla poena sine praevia lege poenali

examples.en: The new rule will be applied retrospectively.
Retrospectively, he seems like a great artist.
Retrospectively, I can see where we went wrong.
Retrospectively, I wished I had never gone to that conference.
We found out only retrospectively that there were many problems.
